claim: Flublok is produced using a novel production platform in which recombinant HA is expressed in insect cells using a baculovirus expression vector system (BEVS).
explanation: A table summarizing demographic characteristics and influenza vaccination history of study participants across four groups (n=122, n=120, n=283, n=198), including mean age, age group distribution, sex, race/ethnicity, study site, and prior vaccination history.
